## 8. API Integration

**The problem:** Every API call needs the auth token in the header. You don't want to manually add the header on every single fetch call.

**Solution: A single API client**

Create `lib/api.ts` — a wrapper around `fetch` that:
1. Automatically adds `Authorization: Bearer <token>`
2. Handles 401 (token expired) → redirect to login
3. Handles errors consistently

Every part of the app imports this one client. The token logic lives in one place.

