## 10. Component Design Philosophy

Three categories of components:

### UI Components (`components/ui/`)
No business logic. No API calls. Just visuals.
- `Button`, `Input`, `Card`, `Badge`, `Spinner`
- Accept props, render HTML

### Feature Components (`components/queue/`, `components/auth/`)
Contain business logic for a specific feature.
- `QueueCard` — displays one queue with join button
- `TokenDisplay` — shows current/my token, connects to WebSocket
- `AdvanceQueuePanel` — operator's "Call Next" interface

### Page Components (`app/**/page.tsx`)
Fetch data, manage page-level state, compose feature components.
- No raw HTML markup
- Just assembles components

